\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\ulnone\f1\fs28 Introduction:\f0\par
\cf0\b0\f2\fs22 Our e-commerce platform is designed to offer high-end home decor items, including vases, designer chairs, elegant mirrors, and premium lamps. This document details the technical framework necessary to create a scalable, user-friendly online marketplace.\cf1\par
\b\fs32 Define Technical Requirements:\par
1. Frontened Requirements:\par
\cf0\b0\fs22 The frontend should deliver an intuitive, visually appealing, and seamless user experience across all devices. The design must prioritize usability, accessibility, and responsiveness to ensure optimal performance on mobile, tablet, and desktop platforms.\fs32\par
