\pard{\pntext\f5\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf5\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b0\f2\fs22 Clean, modern, and visually engaging design that aligns with the brand identity.\par
