\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f1\fs24 2.Responsive Design:\f2\fs20\par

\pard{\pntext\f5\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf5\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\fs22 Fully responsive layout to ensure consistent functionality and aesthetics across all devices (mobile, tablet, and desktop).\par
{\pntext\f5\'B7\tab}Optimized performance for fast loading times and smooth browsing.\par

